  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      61.32,
      632.71,
      575.43,
      678.43
    ],
    "text": "Showers or thundershowers will occur at several places in the sea areas off the coast extending from Kankasanthurai to Hambantota via Puttalam, Colombo and Galle. Showers or thundershowers may occur at a few places elsewhere around the island in the evening or night.",
